data.description: Check out this beautiful 3bd/2.5 bath townhome in Playa Del Sol! 2017 built townhome awaits you with open concept that brings in natural light. SS appliances, kitchen island w/subway backsplashes, & hard wood floors throughout the 2nd level. Corner unit with spacious 2 car garage. Enjoy your morning with a cup of coffee right on your own 2nd story- patio/balcony. Relax your day in the community pool/spa which also features Gym, BBQ area, Clubhouse & playground! Walking Distance to schools & near freeways.
